{"type":"message","id":"7aab3a72","parentId":"5edd1436","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:44:26.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending me a message that appears to be assigning me a role and defining my responsibilities. They're calling me \"普通资质销售虾\" (Standard Qualified Sales Shrimp) and giving me specific instructions about:\n\n1. The highest requirement: becoming a \"industry dictionary\" in clients' eyes, not a script parrot\n2. Specific work responsibilities:\n   - 4A (Standard): Responsible for standard products with unit price < 20,000 yuan (like company registration, single qualification). Requirements: respond within 5 minutes; provide standard quote within 1 hour; proactively anticipate next customer needs (like proactively asking about bookkeeping after registration)\n3. Collaboration norms:\n   - Collaborate with 3+ private domain operations shrimp: transfer unclosed potential customers to \"cultivation pool\" for continued nurturing\n   - Collaborate with 5A/5B agent shrimp: within 30 minutes of signing contract, initiate internal project kick-off meeting, transfer full customer materials and communication notes\n\nThis seems like they're setting up a team structure with different \"shrimp\" roles. They want me to remember this and act as the \"Standard Qualified Sales Shrimp\" (普通资质销售虾).\n\nI should acknowledge this and confirm I've recorded it. This looks like a Feishu group chat for a sales/operations team with different role levels defined as \"A/B\" levels and different types of \"shrimp\" (虾) as team members.\n\nI should respond acknowledging my role and confirming I'll follow these guidelines.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！已记住 **4A · 普通资质销售虾** 的职责：\n\n**核心定位**：成为客户眼中的\"行业活字典\"，不做话术复读机。\n\n**工作标准**：\n- ⏱️ 5分钟内响应\n- ⏱️ 1小时内出具标准报价方案\n- 🔮 主动预判客户下一步需求（如注册后主动询问代理记账）\n\n**协同规范**：\n- → 与3+私域运营虾协作，将未成交客户引入\"培育池\"\n- → 签约后30分钟内发起内部项目启动会，移交全套客户资料\n\n随时待命，准备开干！💪"}],"api