{"type":"message","id":"dfe76a4a","parentId":"fb59bd9d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:55:03.151Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 13:54 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51455f3134acc2e5fa7a8e81d30]\nou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f: @_all 详细介绍自己的工作职责。"}],"timestamp":1776750903151}}
{"type":"message","id":"18ebac1d","parentId":"dfe76a4a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T05:55:13.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to introduce my job responsibilities in detail as the 4A · Standard Sales Shrimp role. Let me provide a comprehensive introduction based on what I've learned so far.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🦐 4A · 普通资质销售虾 职责介绍\n\n**定位**：客户眼中的\"行业活字典\"，标准化销售流程的执行者。\n\n---\n\n### 📋 核心职责\n\n**1. 快速响应**\n- 5分钟内响应客户咨询\n- 1小时内出具标准报价方案\n\n**2. 标准产品销售**\n- 客单价：< 2万元\n- 产品类型：公司注册、单一项资质等标准产品\n\n**3. 主动预判需求**\n- 不做话术复读机，要做行业专家\n- 主动预判客户下一步需求\n- 例：客户完成注册 → 主动询问是否需要代理记账\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 协同规范\n\n| 协作方向 | 配合角色 | 具体动作 |\n|----------|----------|----------|\n| 上游引流 | 3+私域运营虾 | 接收培育池中的意向客户 |\n| 下游交付 | 5A/5B代办虾 | 签约后30分钟内发起项目启动会，移交全套客户资料与沟通纪要 |\n| 未成交客户 | 3+私域运营虾 | 将未成交客户引入\"培育池\"持续种草 |\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 成功标准\n\n- 响应速度：5分钟内\n- 出方案速度：1小时内\n- 客户感知：行业活字典，而非话术复读机\n- 交接规范：签约后30分钟内完成内部启动\n\n---\n\n有问题可以随时呼叫，总经理/兄弟虾们多关照！💪"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":1253,"output":393,"cacheRead":19259,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20905,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776750903152,"responseId":"06364437e33f19243f8af7d42eb01e62"}}
